{"tid":798468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國呼籲各國保障也門平民安全","createTime":"2018-08-29T10:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T12:49:05.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d37946cf42c2b88ae8e13ac4edf1107c17dabec","tid":798468,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】也門的武裝衝突近月升級，聯合國難民署呼籲各國協助在當地的平民。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國難民署發言人指，胡塞武裝控制的紅海港口城市荷台達，自六月起衝突加劇，連串襲擊令超過30萬平民被迫撤離家園。單在本月首九日，已經有逾450名平民被殺，是當地衝突三年半以來死傷最嚴重的時期。他呼籲各方確保平民人身安全，並提供安全路線，讓他們撤離衝突地區。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國日前發表報告指，沙特阿拉伯、阿聯酋和也門交戰各方都涉嫌干犯戰爭行為，包括強姦和虐待平民等。<br />\n<br />\n有份支持沙特阿拉伯在也門發動襲擊的美國國防部長馬蒂斯稱，美國已盡力減少當地的平民傷亡，重申華府支持沙特行使合法權力向胡塞武裝發動空襲，保衛領土。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=318352&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318352%26refer%3D&d=UGuIqBIoNJecAm8OVxanBVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=f3666578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318352%26refer%3D&h=f1e3d99f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=318352&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"cfa3e348f75db9f255cc398b14550ef85a74a062","tid":798468,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:16:38.000Z","msg":"由得啲回教徒自相殘殺啦<br />\n佢哋唔死轉頭咪去玩恐怖襲擊？"},{"pid":"c0d904269c6e5c95c9c980f3a520de6f8769c207","tid":798468,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"好多也門仔黎香港扮難民"},{"pid":"674f3f121dfcaa9fa8cd622693f9a459279e0755","tid":798468,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:18:58.000Z","msg":"This is war!"},{"pid":"08c4d784c22c6970f61d5fb9c3507cd3d5c6d63b","tid":798468,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi